reviews.name: Dingo Market Cuts Chicken Jerky, 16 oz
reviews.reviewText: My dog is part great dane,he enjoyed most treats.When I got these I open them and let him smell of them, he went crazy before I could get him 1 out of the bag. He was a happy dog.Inside the bag you will find large and small pieces. I also gave my cats alittle bit, love it.
reviews.title: Yummy for my Tummy

reviews.name: Dingo Market Cuts Chicken Jerky, 16 oz
reviews.reviewText: These are a little expensive, but my dog loves them. The pieces are large enough to break into 2-3 pieces, so she thinks she's getting more than she is.
reviews.title: Huge pieces, made in USA (SAFE!), dog loves them

reviews.name: Dingo Market Cuts Chicken Jerky, 16 oz
reviews.reviewText: I love my puppy and my puppy loves these.
reviews.title: Excellent

reviews.name: Dingo Market Cuts Chicken Jerky, 16 oz
reviews.reviewText: Dog treats are getting pricey across the board and that includes this one. But it is made in the USA, stays fresh, and the dogs very much enjoy the product as treats, so no complaints.
reviews.title: Pricey, but the dogs like it.

reviews.name: Dingo Market Cuts Chicken Jerky, 16 oz
reviews.reviewText:
real chicken, but very small pieces and not full size jerky piece like I usually get with others brands.
